{"tid":2492283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：疫情令印度疫苗需求增　影響全球供應","createTime":"2021-04-17T04:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T09:37:14.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf42d9bbfe317d36c0eacfdbbbb671a6b9d9e92","tid":2492283,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"印度搶疫苗，中國不高興，港台要出聲<br />\n<br />\n印度的新型肺炎疫情持續惡化，過去兩日新增確診個案都超過20萬宗，連續兩日創單日新高，仍然是全球第二多感染病例的國家，當局形容是當地的第三波疫情。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指出，一向有對外輸出新型冠狀病毒疫苗的印度，近日意識到當地疫苗不足的情況，開始從外國進口新冠疫苗，<strong>有評論憂慮印度對疫苗龐大的需求，會打亂全球疫苗的供應鏈。</strong><br />\n<br />\n有印度確診患者因為等不到公營醫院的診治，購買黑市的醫療用品或藥物，令疫情可能更難控制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586283-20210417.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586283-20210417.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=5ecad951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586283-20210417.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=167e85a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586283-20210417.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f4c865cd87ebfa6d49389a1b82b5d711c7193a3b","tid":2492283,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:37:14.000Z","msg":"送啲科興俾佢"}]}